OL,3,CHow a building once called 'Britain's
OL,4,Cugliest' is now officially protected
OL,6,FThe Southbank Centre sits in the heart
OL,7,Fof London and its origins date back to
OL,8,Fthe Festival of Britain which promoted
OL,9,Fa sense of renewal after the Second
OL,10,FWorld War.
OL,12,FThe Royal Festival Hall, which already
OL,13,Fhas Grade I listed status, was first
OL,14,Fto be built followed by the rest of
OL,15,Fthe complex over a decade later.
