OL,3,CHow a building once called 'Britain's
OL,4,Cugliest' is now officially protected
OL,6,F"Alongside the Grade I listed Royal
OL,7,FFestival Hall, the Southbank Centre
OL,8,Fhas asked the Government for #30
OL,9,Fmillion to support improvements to our
OL,10,Finfrastructure in our 75th anniversary.
OL,12,F"We look forward to working with the
OL,13,FGovernment to ensure these buildings
OL,14,Fare able to thrive long into the
OL,15,Ffuture."
OL,17,FCampaign group The Twentieth Century
OL,18,FSociety celebrated the Grade II listed
OL,19,Fstatus after launching a bid to secure
OL,20,Fprotection.
