OL,3,CHow a building once called 'Britain's
OL,4,Cugliest' is now officially protected
OL,6,FThey described the site as "visionary"
OL,7,Fand a "masterpiece" and perhaps the
OL,8,Fmost totemic and controversial example
OL,9,Fof British Brutalism.
OL,11,FThe Southbank Centre has been
OL,12,Frecommended for listing six times
OL,13,Fsince 1991 but always rejected by the
OL,14,FSecretary of State, until now.
OL,16,F"The decision brings to an end an
OL,17,Funprecedented 35 year-long impasse,
OL,18,Fone of the longest running battles in
OL,19,FBritish architectural heritage," The
OL,20,FTwentieth Century Society said.
