OL,3,CHow a building once called 'Britain's
OL,4,Cugliest' is now officially protected
OL,6,FSouthbank Centre: Key milestones
OL,7,Ftimeline
OL,9,FThe tabloid press famously called the
OL,10,FHayward Gallery 'Britain's ugliest
OL,11,Fbuilding' shortly after it opened in
OL,12,Fthe 1960s, reflecting the strong
OL,13,Fpublic backlash against Brutalist
OL,14,Farchitecture at the time.
OL,16,FThe phrase stuck in popular culture
OL,17,Fand contributed to the perception of
OL,18,Fthe Southbank Centre as controversial,
OL,19,Feven though architects and cultural
OL,20,Fcommentators defended its bold design.
