OL,3,CHow a building once called 'Britain's
OL,4,Cugliest' is now officially protected
OL,6,FCatherine Croft, Director of Twentieth
OL,7,FCentury Society said: "The battle has
OL,8,Fbeen won and Brutalism has finally
OL,9,Fcome of age.
OL,11,F"This is a victory over those who
OL,12,Fderided so called 'concrete
OL,13,Fmonstrosities' and shows a mature
OL,14,Frecognition of a style where Britain
OL,15,Fled the way.
