OL,6,F"We're absolutely thrilled that this
OL,7,Finternationally recognised concrete-
OL,8,Fmasterpiece of post-war architecture
OL,9,Fhas finally been accepted as part of
OL,10,Four national heritage, some 35 years
OL,11,Fafter the Twentieth Century Society
OL,12,Ffirst campaigned for the Southbank
OL,13,FCentre to be protected."
